    <!-- Privacy and Permissions -->
    <string name="privacy_policy">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_agreement_title">Privacy Agreement</string>
    <string name="privacy_agreement_content">This application collects sensor data (accelerometer, gyroscope, magnetometer) and usage statistics for continuous authentication research purposes.\n\n• Data Collection: Motion sensor data is collected only when the device is unlocked and the app is active.\n\n• Data Processing: All data is encrypted immediately using AES-256-GCM encryption before temporary storage.\n\n• Data Storage: Encrypted data is temporarily cached in the app\'s private directory and deleted after successful upload.\n\n• Data Transmission: Data is transmitted securely using TLS 1.3 encryption to research servers.\n\n• Data Usage: Collected data is used solely for academic research on continuous authentication systems.\n\n• Data Sharing: Data is not shared with third parties and is used only for specified research purposes.\n\n• User Rights: You can revoke consent and delete all collected data at any time by uninstalling the application.\n\nBy continuing, you consent to this data collection and processing.</string>
